WEBVTT

01:43.080 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

01:50.080 --> 01:51.640
Sangsang, help me take a look.

01:51.720 --> 01:53.040
Does this long, wide-angle shot

01:53.120 --> 01:54.480
look out of place?

01:55.120 --> 01:57.160
It makes this spot look weird.

01:57.240 --> 01:58.080
This spot isn't good.

01:58.160 --> 01:59.960
The next static shot seems off.

02:00.040 --> 02:01.960
What if I put the subtitle above it?

02:02.040 --> 02:03.840
- Yes, swap them.
- Swap them? Okay.

02:03.920 --> 02:05.160
Do you want a drink?

02:05.240 --> 02:06.080
- No.
- No?

02:07.000 --> 02:07.840
Fruit.

02:07.920 --> 02:09.759
Swap the two.

02:09.840 --> 02:10.720
Okay.

02:13.720 --> 02:14.960
- Apple?
- Thank you.

02:17.800 --> 02:19.680
- Take a look inside.
- Okay.

02:21.240 --> 02:23.440
This used to be an event venue
for a company.

02:23.520 --> 02:26.520
It will be perfect as a workspace.

02:26.600 --> 02:29.840
And is the balcony back there included?

02:29.920 --> 02:31.680
Yes, it's included.

02:31.760 --> 02:33.960
This space is around
200 square meters in total.

02:35.480 --> 02:37.240
Jiaxu, this office is smaller

02:37.320 --> 02:39.080
than the previous one.

02:39.640 --> 02:41.560
It is 150 square meters.

02:42.560 --> 02:45.000
- 150 square meters?
- It is closer to your expectation.

02:45.080 --> 02:46.880
It's ready to go

02:46.960 --> 02:48.120
once your employees relocate.

02:49.240 --> 02:51.480
- Is this a conference room?
- Yes.

02:51.560 --> 02:53.280
Is the price negotiable?

02:54.040 --> 02:56.680
Yes, because the landlord wants
to support young entrepreneurs.

02:56.760 --> 02:58.000
That's wonderful.

02:58.600 --> 02:59.760
How about this?

03:00.320 --> 03:01.240
It works.

03:01.320 --> 03:02.400
- It can work.
- Look at this.

03:03.360 --> 03:04.720
This is so cute!

03:04.800 --> 03:06.480
I'll use this angle then.

03:06.560 --> 03:08.560
Don't criticize me.

03:08.640 --> 03:10.040
I didn't!

03:10.920 --> 03:12.320
- Sorry!
- Enough!

03:12.400 --> 03:13.640
- Sorry.
- Okay, that's enough.

03:14.360 --> 03:16.280
- Come on. Continue.
- Fine, I'll let it go for you.

03:16.360 --> 03:17.520
Good job.

03:19.280 --> 03:20.840
- Have some water.
- Thank you, sir.

03:21.400 --> 03:22.720
Where do I put this, sir?

03:22.800 --> 03:24.360
Put that in the room first.

03:28.440 --> 03:29.800
Okay, thank you.

03:29.880 --> 03:30.920
It's all set, right?

03:39.960 --> 03:41.040
Liu Yu, right?

03:41.120 --> 03:42.160
- Yes, that's me.
- Hi.

03:42.240 --> 03:43.360
- Hi.
- Hi.

03:43.440 --> 03:44.440
- Have a seat.
- Okay.

03:45.200 --> 03:46.040
Thank you for waiting.

03:46.120 --> 03:47.120
No problem.

03:48.560 --> 03:49.840
This is my resume.

03:49.920 --> 03:51.200
Please have a look.

03:51.280 --> 03:52.680
- It looks so formal.
- Yes.

03:54.000 --> 03:56.520
Have you played A Dream of Jianghu before?

03:56.600 --> 03:57.480
Yes.

03:57.560 --> 03:59.800
I'm really impressed
with the optimized version.

03:59.880 --> 04:01.480
You flatter me.

04:01.560 --> 04:03.360
This is my start-up's early stage.

04:03.440 --> 04:04.560
Let's learn from each other.

04:12.200 --> 04:13.040
Try it.

04:14.160 --> 04:16.040
CONGRATULATIONS,
YOUR SUBMISSION WAS SUCCESSFUL

04:17.040 --> 04:18.760
It's done. You can rest now.

04:19.800 --> 04:20.680
I'm free.

04:25.560 --> 04:28.120
CHAPTER 25, RUN TOWARDS YOU

04:28.200 --> 04:30.200
SECRETLY, UNABLE TO HIDE IT

04:31.800 --> 04:32.880
Put it on my tab.

04:32.960 --> 04:36.080
Sang Yan's bar has quite the ambiance.

04:36.160 --> 04:37.440
The bar called Syria is nice too.

04:37.520 --> 04:38.400
Here, have some cola.

04:41.640 --> 04:42.800
I'll sit with you, Qian Fei.

04:43.960 --> 04:45.200
Why?

04:45.680 --> 04:48.080
We should keep some distance,

04:48.720 --> 04:50.400
so my girlfriend doesn't get
the wrong idea.

04:51.200 --> 04:52.360
Screw you.

04:56.440 --> 04:57.320
There you are.

04:58.360 --> 05:00.480
Yes, at long last! I am exhausted.

05:00.560 --> 05:01.800
You even have your luggage.

05:01.880 --> 05:02.760
I'm dead tired.

05:04.400 --> 05:06.480
Slow down. Are you that hungry?

05:06.560 --> 05:09.160
I rushed here after I got off the plane.

05:09.240 --> 05:10.400
I'll faint from hunger.

05:10.480 --> 05:11.480
I appreciate it, Junwen.

05:11.560 --> 05:13.280
Thank you for coming to be
my chief programmer.

05:13.840 --> 05:15.720
Order whatever you want.

05:15.800 --> 05:17.000
It's your welcoming party.

05:17.640 --> 05:19.280
We have the boss here anyway.

05:21.600 --> 05:23.080
- I'll go all out then.
- Order away.

05:23.160 --> 05:24.000
Scan the code.

05:26.280 --> 05:27.880
Speaking of which,

05:28.480 --> 05:30.720
I came to help you with your start-up,

05:30.800 --> 05:32.720
but you didn't even come to pick me up.

05:33.360 --> 05:35.160
Excuse me?

05:36.360 --> 05:38.520
They were your college roommates too.

05:38.600 --> 05:39.640
They didn't pick you up.

05:39.720 --> 05:41.240
Don't just blame me.

05:42.280 --> 05:43.800
He's right. You two didn't pick me up.

05:43.880 --> 05:44.760
Why is that?

05:46.800 --> 05:48.040
I…

05:48.840 --> 05:49.800
Sorry.

05:52.040 --> 05:52.880
Sang Yan.

05:53.560 --> 05:54.680
I would like

05:55.880 --> 05:57.880
to visit your parents
in the next few days.

05:59.680 --> 06:00.880
Are you so eager

06:00.960 --> 06:03.120
to meet her parents already?

06:03.760 --> 06:04.960
That's not it.

06:05.040 --> 06:06.320
I finally have some free time

06:06.400 --> 06:07.760
after being busy with my studio.

06:07.840 --> 06:09.640
I think I should visit them.

06:10.240 --> 06:12.000
I want to discuss something with them.

06:13.800 --> 06:14.720
He's not like you.

06:14.800 --> 06:17.160
He dates with marriage as the goal.

06:17.240 --> 06:18.800
He doesn't string girls along.

06:18.880 --> 06:20.080
You even tell them,

06:20.160 --> 06:21.360
"All the girls chase after me."

06:21.920 --> 06:24.000
You are 125 kg of bull crap.

06:24.080 --> 06:25.240
Shut it.

06:25.320 --> 06:26.280
Who is 125kg?

06:26.360 --> 06:27.440
Who? Me?

06:32.240 --> 06:34.040
Duan Jiaxu, you have changed.

06:34.560 --> 06:36.600
You're no longer
the Duan Jiaxu who liked me.

06:37.160 --> 06:38.840
Listen, my circumstances have changed.

06:38.920 --> 06:40.120
My brother-in-law

06:40.200 --> 06:41.600
is sitting across from me.

06:41.680 --> 06:43.080
I have to take his side.

06:43.160 --> 06:44.760
Right, darling brother?

06:46.480 --> 06:47.840
- Darling brother!
- Darling brother!

06:47.920 --> 06:49.840
Wait. After dating my sister,

06:49.920 --> 06:50.840
you're as dumb as her.

06:51.640 --> 06:53.040
My brother is so mean.

06:53.120 --> 06:54.240
How mean!

06:54.320 --> 06:56.560
- Yes!
- He's so harsh!

07:05.840 --> 07:06.960
SANG ZHI

07:07.040 --> 07:07.920
Do you mind?

07:08.560 --> 07:09.720
- Yes.
- Yes.

07:12.720 --> 07:13.600
Hello?

07:13.680 --> 07:15.840
Hello. Are you still out?

07:15.920 --> 07:16.800
Yes.

07:17.360 --> 07:19.040
Chen Junwen arrived today.

07:19.120 --> 07:21.560
Sang Yan, Qian Fei, and I

07:21.640 --> 07:23.160
threw him a welcoming party.

07:23.720 --> 07:24.840
Are you back at your dorm?

07:26.240 --> 07:27.280
Yes, I'm back.

07:27.360 --> 07:29.680
Call me when you get home later.

07:32.640 --> 07:34.280
Okay, I'll call you when I'm home.

07:35.240 --> 07:36.120
By the way,

07:36.760 --> 07:37.600
don't worry.

07:37.680 --> 07:39.520
Nothing is going on
between me and those three.

07:41.680 --> 07:43.280
Are they next to you?

07:43.880 --> 07:45.160
Yes.

07:46.200 --> 07:48.480
Then tell them that I'm jealous.

07:48.960 --> 07:49.880
Bye.

07:52.600 --> 07:54.840
Now I know why you two are going

07:54.920 --> 07:56.200
to be family.

07:56.280 --> 07:57.440
You two are just the same.

07:57.520 --> 07:58.920
Don't drag me into this.

08:00.160 --> 08:01.560
I seem to remember

08:02.480 --> 08:04.320
that someone told his sister

08:04.400 --> 08:07.080
that every girl in our school

08:07.160 --> 08:08.120
was obsessed with him.

08:08.200 --> 08:09.880
Who could possibly be this narcissistic?

08:09.960 --> 08:11.320
Who is so shameless?

08:11.400 --> 08:12.800
Yes, who are you talking about?

08:12.880 --> 08:13.760
Indeed.

08:13.840 --> 08:16.160
That's on you, darling brother.

08:17.040 --> 08:18.480
- Darling brother!
- Darling brother!

08:18.560 --> 08:19.560
Enough. Shut up.

08:21.360 --> 08:22.400
When are you coming?

08:23.840 --> 08:25.680
Pick a time when your parents are free.

08:25.760 --> 08:27.080
Why?

08:27.160 --> 08:28.200
I'll join in on the fun.

08:29.920 --> 08:30.880
Me too.

08:30.960 --> 08:31.800
Count me in.

08:31.880 --> 08:32.919
Get lost!

08:33.480 --> 08:34.520
Don't be nosy, you two.

08:35.919 --> 08:36.799
Why can't I come?

08:36.880 --> 08:37.960
I'll come if I want to.

08:38.440 --> 08:40.360
Let's not tease them. Eat this.

09:06.600 --> 09:07.920
You're punctual.

09:12.080 --> 09:13.240
You were serious about coming.

09:13.320 --> 09:14.200
Of course.

09:14.280 --> 09:15.840
Because Sang Zhi said

09:15.920 --> 09:17.320
that our parents don't like you,

09:17.400 --> 09:18.920
so I'm here to see if that's true.

09:19.000 --> 09:20.080
Then I can mock you.

09:22.320 --> 09:24.000
You are all dressed up.

09:24.080 --> 09:26.160
Just sit by the side and watch.

09:26.240 --> 09:27.160
Don't say anything.

09:29.040 --> 09:30.880
I'm staying out of it.

09:30.960 --> 09:32.240
I wouldn't be here

09:32.320 --> 09:33.760
if Sang Zhi hadn't asked me to help.

09:35.080 --> 09:36.000
Come in.

09:44.720 --> 09:45.800
Xiaoduan, hello.

09:46.560 --> 09:47.960
It has been a while, Mrs. Sang.

09:48.440 --> 09:50.160
I bought you and Mr. Sang some food.

09:51.080 --> 09:52.320
Why? No need for that.

09:52.400 --> 09:53.760
- Keep it.
- No.

09:53.840 --> 09:55.440
Please accept it. I insist.

09:55.520 --> 09:56.760
Take it.

09:56.840 --> 09:58.240
He can bring it in.

09:58.320 --> 09:59.960
- I've got it.
- Then I'll get it.

10:00.640 --> 10:02.960
Mom, I'll get it.

10:05.120 --> 10:06.280
My husband is cooking.

10:06.360 --> 10:07.800
It will be ready soon. Take a seat.

10:07.880 --> 10:08.920
- Okay.
- Okay.

10:09.000 --> 10:10.160
- Go ahead.
- Okay.

10:34.000 --> 10:34.960
It's delicious.

10:40.920 --> 10:41.920
Xiaoduan.

10:42.520 --> 10:45.080
Have you found a place for your studio?

10:46.000 --> 10:46.880
Yes.

10:46.960 --> 10:49.040
It's in our headquarters' technology park.

10:49.120 --> 10:50.520
I've already assembled my team.

10:51.160 --> 10:52.640
That's a nice environment.

10:52.720 --> 10:54.080
It's perfect for a start-up.

10:54.160 --> 10:55.000
Yes.

10:55.080 --> 10:57.240
We will head into full operation soon.

10:57.840 --> 10:59.000
Good.

10:59.080 --> 11:00.320
Eat some more.

11:00.400 --> 11:01.280
Sure.

11:10.960 --> 11:12.120
Mr. and Mrs. Sang,

11:12.200 --> 11:13.680
I have to use the restroom.

11:13.760 --> 11:14.600
Enjoy the meal.

11:14.680 --> 11:15.520
It's upstairs.

11:31.680 --> 11:33.320
Here, have some fruit.

11:33.400 --> 11:35.840
- Thank you.
- Xiaoduan, are you full?

11:35.920 --> 11:37.000
Yes.

11:37.080 --> 11:38.240
You didn't eat a lot.

11:38.320 --> 11:39.720
Was the meal not to your liking?

11:39.800 --> 11:41.760
No, it was very delicious.

11:41.840 --> 11:43.080
I'm glad to hear that.

11:43.640 --> 11:44.880
Try this amazing tea.

11:44.960 --> 11:46.320
- Thank you, Mr. Sang.
- Do you want any?

11:46.400 --> 11:47.240
No, thank you.

11:48.360 --> 11:49.840
Just drink it.

11:49.920 --> 11:51.640
Ignore him. Enjoy the tea.

11:55.280 --> 11:56.280
Mr. Sang.

11:57.120 --> 11:59.120
I have thought a lot about the concerns

11:59.200 --> 12:02.040
that you mentioned last time.

12:03.160 --> 12:04.640
I understand

12:04.720 --> 12:06.520
why you have misgivings

12:06.600 --> 12:07.960
about my relationship with Zhizhi.

12:08.680 --> 12:11.120
You are afraid she will be hurt.

12:12.360 --> 12:14.240
But I'm here to tell you

12:14.320 --> 12:16.080
that I'm very serious about Sang Zhi.

12:20.640 --> 12:21.680
You see,

12:22.520 --> 12:23.960
after my dad's car accident,

12:24.040 --> 12:25.440
the victim's family

12:25.520 --> 12:27.040
did come to pester us.

12:27.760 --> 12:29.480
However, it has been fully dealt with now.

12:30.320 --> 12:31.920
You need not worry about it anymore.

12:35.120 --> 12:37.680
Sang Zhi will graduate in two years.

12:37.760 --> 12:39.440
Before that, I will work here

12:39.520 --> 12:41.080
for my future and hers.

12:43.880 --> 12:44.920
Are you sure

12:45.560 --> 12:47.200
you want to start over in Nanwu?

12:47.960 --> 12:48.880
Yes.

12:48.960 --> 12:50.160
Mr. and Mrs. Sang.

12:51.080 --> 12:52.600
I would be a different person

12:53.160 --> 12:56.080
if I had never met Sang Zhi.

13:00.160 --> 13:01.920
I heard from Sang Yan that you work.

13:02.480 --> 13:03.960
Then I see you working today.

13:05.560 --> 13:06.600
I wanted to say

13:06.680 --> 13:08.040
that you don't have to treat me

13:08.120 --> 13:09.400
if you're short on cash.

13:14.560 --> 13:15.680
Jiaxu.

13:15.760 --> 13:17.120
Don't panic.

13:17.800 --> 13:19.240
Once I grow up

13:19.320 --> 13:20.320
and start making money,

13:20.400 --> 13:21.520
I'll help you pay it off.

13:23.920 --> 13:25.240
She always puts me first

13:26.320 --> 13:27.560
in everything she does.

13:32.560 --> 13:33.480
Jiang Ying!

13:38.480 --> 13:39.560
Does it hurt?

13:40.040 --> 13:41.560
It's not a major surgery.

13:42.280 --> 13:43.560
- It's okay.
- I'll wait for you.

13:44.520 --> 13:46.400
She is clearly much younger than me.

13:47.160 --> 13:49.000
I should be the one protecting her,

13:49.480 --> 13:51.560
yet she always wants to shield me.

13:55.080 --> 13:56.640
As long as I am here,

13:58.400 --> 14:00.920
I won't let anyone bully Duan Jiaxu again.

14:03.720 --> 14:05.680
He has me

14:07.800 --> 14:09.560
and many others who love him.

14:11.880 --> 14:13.160
We all love you.

14:15.360 --> 14:17.320
She helped me overcome my past,

14:18.440 --> 14:19.400
and I will

14:20.000 --> 14:21.480
safeguard her future.

14:25.000 --> 14:26.120
Mr. and Mrs. Sang.

14:27.080 --> 14:29.920
I don't have a lot in my possession.

14:31.040 --> 14:32.560
But I will give my all

14:33.960 --> 14:35.360
to treat Zhizhi well for a lifetime.

14:40.960 --> 14:41.880
Jiaxu.

14:42.560 --> 14:44.760
We see your sincerity.

14:46.440 --> 14:48.840
Zhizhi has mentioned
her relationship with you

14:48.920 --> 14:51.360
to us many times.

14:51.440 --> 14:53.480
As it was only her side of the story,

14:53.560 --> 14:55.160
we were unsure about the whole thing.

14:55.240 --> 14:56.440
Previously,

14:56.520 --> 14:58.960
we said that we were worried

14:59.040 --> 14:59.960
about your family.

15:00.600 --> 15:03.360
That was because we didn't want Zhizhi
to get hurt.

15:03.440 --> 15:05.880
If you say that you can protect her,

15:05.960 --> 15:07.360
that's all we want to hear

15:07.840 --> 15:09.240
as her parents.

15:11.960 --> 15:13.120
Xiaoduan.

15:13.680 --> 15:15.760
My husband and I really want…

15:16.640 --> 15:17.560
In fact,

15:18.200 --> 15:19.200
it all boils down

15:20.760 --> 15:22.200
to her happiness.

15:22.720 --> 15:23.560
Yes.

15:23.640 --> 15:25.680
The rest isn't an issue.

15:27.920 --> 15:28.880
I know.

15:34.400 --> 15:36.120
Now I finally understand

15:37.360 --> 15:39.320
why Zhizhi is so amazing.

15:41.080 --> 15:42.240
She is so lucky

15:43.280 --> 15:45.280
to have the two of you as her parents.

15:50.560 --> 15:52.920
Did you forget

15:53.520 --> 15:54.640
about her awesome brother?

15:56.360 --> 15:57.440
What?

15:58.160 --> 15:59.600
Don't be narcissistic.

16:00.920 --> 16:02.040
I'm part of the family too.

16:02.520 --> 16:03.360
Have tea, Xiaoduan.

16:03.440 --> 16:04.920
- I'm her brother.
- Thank you, Mrs. Sang.

16:07.800 --> 16:09.800
Does the little demon know
that you met the parents?

16:11.400 --> 16:12.520
I haven't told her yet.

16:14.720 --> 16:16.760
Listen, as a man,

16:16.840 --> 16:18.480
you need to toughen up.

16:18.560 --> 16:20.920
Did you hear what you said earlier?

16:21.000 --> 16:21.920
What's wrong?

16:22.000 --> 16:23.240
If you spoil her like that,

16:23.320 --> 16:25.240
I can envision your future.

16:26.560 --> 16:27.840
She will be the death of you.

16:27.920 --> 16:29.440
And if you spoil her rotten,

16:29.520 --> 16:30.600
she'll take it for granted

16:30.680 --> 16:31.880
and feel entitled.

16:32.600 --> 16:33.760
I don't mind it.

16:34.480 --> 16:35.680
One more thing.

16:36.440 --> 16:37.320
From now on,

16:37.840 --> 16:39.480
don't take everything on yourself.

16:39.560 --> 16:40.960
It's so unreasonable.

16:41.600 --> 16:42.560
You can

16:44.280 --> 16:45.280
make your life easier.

16:51.000 --> 16:52.120
Thank you, buddy.

16:54.240 --> 16:55.200
I'm serious.

16:55.760 --> 16:57.000
Thank you

16:59.200 --> 17:00.160
for all you've done.

17:02.440 --> 17:03.600
You're crazy.

17:13.440 --> 17:15.880
I remember the first time I met Sang Zhi.

17:16.960 --> 17:19.640
We were walking on this street
to take out the trash.

17:25.800 --> 17:27.480
Your sister should be quite obedient.

17:28.920 --> 17:29.920
Obedient?

17:30.480 --> 17:31.720
She's in her rebellious phase.

17:31.800 --> 17:32.800
She won't listen to me.

17:32.880 --> 17:35.320
You've seen how my parents spoil her.

17:35.400 --> 17:36.360
She's in middle school,

17:36.440 --> 17:38.120
but acts like
an elementary school student.

17:39.520 --> 17:40.480
Is that so?

17:42.200 --> 17:43.320
I have something to tell you.

17:44.720 --> 17:46.760
Your sister's teacher wants
to see your parents.

17:46.840 --> 17:49.400
She kept asking me
if I could see the teacher for her.

17:49.480 --> 17:51.640
Jiaxu, are you coming or not tomorrow?

17:51.720 --> 17:53.000
I've told you everything.

17:53.600 --> 17:55.120
Why don't you ask Sang Yan?

17:55.200 --> 17:56.440
No way!

17:57.080 --> 17:58.680
I framed him just now.

17:59.240 --> 18:00.360
So Sang Zhi.

18:00.440 --> 18:02.400
You know when we'll meet next time, right?

18:04.480 --> 18:05.840
Bye.

18:08.080 --> 18:09.560
Close the gate when you leave.

18:15.040 --> 18:16.520
Go and see her teacher tomorrow.

18:17.840 --> 18:20.320
So that's why she insisted
on inviting you to dinner.

18:20.400 --> 18:21.960
She had a secret agenda.

18:23.720 --> 18:25.680
It's probably nothing serious.

18:25.760 --> 18:28.240
It's always the same problem
when the teacher wants to see us.

18:31.280 --> 18:32.480
She needs to learn her lesson.

18:32.560 --> 18:33.720
I won't indulge her this time.

18:33.800 --> 18:34.960
Ignore her.

18:35.640 --> 18:38.040
No, I just promised her.

18:40.600 --> 18:42.360
I can go with you tomorrow.

18:42.440 --> 18:43.480
It's just a simple meeting.

18:43.560 --> 18:45.040
You promised her. I didn't.

18:45.120 --> 18:45.960
Go on your own.

18:49.960 --> 18:51.720
She followed me to the front door

18:52.880 --> 18:54.640
just to secretly confirm

18:55.320 --> 18:57.080
if I'll see the teacher for her.

19:00.320 --> 19:01.320
I forgot about it already.

19:03.280 --> 19:04.920
Slow down, darling brother.

19:37.120 --> 19:38.280
Aren't I punctual?

19:44.280 --> 19:45.520
Are you not in your dorm?

19:46.800 --> 19:48.800
I went home

19:49.360 --> 19:51.000
because I have no classes
tomorrow morning.

19:51.080 --> 19:52.040
I figured

19:52.120 --> 19:54.160
I could come here to snack.

19:54.240 --> 19:56.480
And tomorrow, I can sleep in.

19:59.840 --> 20:00.760
Who is this?

20:02.800 --> 20:04.000
What happened?

20:04.080 --> 20:05.720
You seem extra chirpy today.

20:09.440 --> 20:10.360
I am quite happy.

20:11.160 --> 20:12.280
Happy about what?

20:19.960 --> 20:20.880
Tell me.

20:25.920 --> 20:26.960
Well, here's the thing.

20:29.920 --> 20:31.440
I went to see your parents today.

20:32.040 --> 20:33.160
And then

20:35.440 --> 20:36.560
they gave their approval.

20:37.640 --> 20:39.640
How did you convince them?

20:39.720 --> 20:41.080
What did they say?

20:41.160 --> 20:43.440
Did they say they support us now?

20:43.520 --> 20:44.400
Really?

20:44.480 --> 20:45.720
Are you happy?

20:46.280 --> 20:47.160
I'm very happy.

20:47.680 --> 20:48.640
Me too.

20:50.280 --> 20:51.400
Listen.

20:51.480 --> 20:53.280
From now on,

20:53.360 --> 20:54.760
you must be even more certain

20:54.840 --> 20:56.040
that you're the best.

20:56.680 --> 20:58.000
You, Duan Jiaxu,

20:58.080 --> 20:59.480
are the best in the world.

21:00.000 --> 21:02.360
And no one can tell you otherwise.

21:02.440 --> 21:03.360
Got it?

21:06.160 --> 21:07.320
I miss you so much.

21:08.680 --> 21:09.960
I miss you too.

21:15.120 --> 21:16.400
That's right.

21:18.320 --> 21:20.480
Are you free at the end of the month?

21:20.560 --> 21:21.680
The end of the month?

21:21.760 --> 21:22.720
Why?

21:28.320 --> 21:31.120
My design won an award.

21:31.200 --> 21:33.080
The award ceremony is
at the end of the month.

21:33.160 --> 21:34.000
That's amazing!

21:35.400 --> 21:36.520
Will you come?

21:36.600 --> 21:39.400
When did you say it is?

21:40.120 --> 21:41.240
The end of the month.

21:43.680 --> 21:46.320
That might be a bit hard to arrange.

21:47.560 --> 21:48.440
You see,

21:48.520 --> 21:50.840
I have a new project at the moment,

21:50.920 --> 21:52.640
so I have a lot of meetings to attend.

21:52.720 --> 21:54.240
The end of the month is…

21:57.640 --> 21:58.840
I'm sorry.

21:58.920 --> 22:01.240
It's okay. Focus on your work.

22:01.320 --> 22:02.840
Well…

22:04.160 --> 22:06.360
The next time I win an award,

22:06.440 --> 22:07.640
you have to be there.

22:07.720 --> 22:08.880
Pinky promise?

22:11.240 --> 22:12.080
Pinky promise.

22:12.680 --> 22:14.880
Whoever breaks the promise
is a big, fat dummy.

22:45.640 --> 22:47.040
Has the ceremony started?

22:49.520 --> 22:51.280
Is your boyfriend not coming today?

22:54.960 --> 22:55.880
He's busy.

22:58.560 --> 23:00.640
That's true. I can imagine.

23:01.120 --> 23:03.240
Don't forget about me, future CEO's wife.

23:04.200 --> 23:05.360
Show me the previous one.

23:07.000 --> 23:07.880
This one?

23:07.960 --> 23:09.160
No, this one.

23:17.440 --> 23:18.400
Why are you ignoring me?

23:23.560 --> 23:24.840
Do it like this.

23:29.680 --> 23:31.240
Who is that?

23:31.320 --> 23:32.400
He's so handsome.

23:32.480 --> 23:33.840
Who is he? He's a hunk.

23:33.920 --> 23:34.800
He's so cute.

23:37.520 --> 23:38.720
Miss.

23:39.440 --> 23:41.040
Why did you ignore your boyfriend's text?

23:45.800 --> 23:46.800
Is this seat taken?

23:46.880 --> 23:48.080
No.

23:48.160 --> 23:49.360
Sit down.

23:52.880 --> 23:53.760
It has been a while.

23:53.840 --> 23:54.800
It certainly has been.

23:57.480 --> 23:59.040
Why are you here?

23:59.120 --> 24:01.720
DUAN JIAXU

24:01.800 --> 24:03.200
Why do you react like this?

24:04.240 --> 24:06.000
It feels like you don't miss me at all.

24:13.800 --> 24:15.760
When did you get here?

24:15.840 --> 24:18.720
SANG ZHI

24:19.400 --> 24:20.680
My flight was this morning.

24:22.920 --> 24:24.560
So why are you here?

24:24.640 --> 24:26.480
SANG ZHI

24:26.560 --> 24:27.840
DUAN JIAXU

24:27.920 --> 24:29.920
I know you're coming
to this award ceremony.

24:30.000 --> 24:32.400
The A Dream of Jianghu team
was also invited.

24:32.920 --> 24:34.920
I came in Siyun's place.

24:39.040 --> 24:40.320
Then why did you say

24:40.400 --> 24:41.440
that you weren't coming?

24:43.960 --> 24:45.080
I wanted

24:46.000 --> 24:47.000
to give you a surprise.

24:52.240 --> 24:54.720
I saw it in your guide.

24:55.400 --> 24:56.840
Frequent surprises are necessary

24:56.920 --> 24:58.600
in maintaining
a long-distance relationship.

25:00.480 --> 25:01.800
I thought you forgot.

25:02.480 --> 25:03.520
How is that possible?

25:04.320 --> 25:05.960
It's my phone wallpaper.

25:09.480 --> 25:11.720
When you said you weren't coming,

25:11.800 --> 25:12.640
I…

25:15.320 --> 25:16.320
Were you disappointed?

25:17.720 --> 25:18.720
Unhappy?

25:19.920 --> 25:21.800
- Don't tell me you cried.
- No.

25:25.160 --> 25:26.680
I am very happy that you could come.

25:31.720 --> 25:33.320
Why am I sitting here?

25:33.400 --> 25:34.840
They're sickeningly sweet!

25:35.360 --> 25:36.840
Is it Sangsang and her boyfriend?

25:37.400 --> 25:38.920
I want to see!

25:47.480 --> 25:48.760
Should we sit in the back?

25:55.120 --> 25:56.360
Sorry to bother you.

25:57.520 --> 25:58.480
Let's go.

26:01.000 --> 26:02.200
Sorry to disturb you, miss.

26:03.800 --> 26:04.840
Sorry, miss.

26:05.920 --> 26:06.840
Hurry up.

26:06.920 --> 26:08.720
- Excuse me.
- Hurry up.

26:40.280 --> 26:41.960
Did you change into a suit for this?

26:43.240 --> 26:44.320
How does it look?

26:44.400 --> 26:46.320
Does this tie go with this suit?

26:50.600 --> 26:51.680
But today,

26:52.320 --> 26:54.000
the tie feels a little tight.

26:54.080 --> 26:55.240
It's strangling me.

26:56.560 --> 26:58.000
You have to button this…

27:08.000 --> 27:09.200
- What are--
- What are you doing?

27:12.280 --> 27:13.960
If you want to kiss me, just say so.

27:14.480 --> 27:16.120
No need for these little tricks.

27:19.880 --> 27:20.720
I…

27:41.800 --> 27:42.640
What's wrong?

27:44.840 --> 27:47.320
Was I too shameless?

27:49.200 --> 27:50.160
So you know.

27:57.520 --> 27:58.360
Sorry.

27:59.880 --> 28:01.800
I just haven't seen you for too long.

28:03.280 --> 28:04.480
I really miss you.

28:14.000 --> 28:14.920
What?

28:16.000 --> 28:17.360
What does that mean?

28:18.760 --> 28:19.880
That means

28:23.000 --> 28:24.280
that I miss you too.

28:32.440 --> 28:34.520
Mr. Duan, may I trouble you for a second?

28:37.640 --> 28:38.840
I'm going to sign in.

28:41.600 --> 28:42.440
Wait a moment.

28:55.040 --> 28:56.320
Wait for me.

29:04.920 --> 29:06.920
Next up, we will award

29:07.000 --> 29:08.720
the final prize

29:08.800 --> 29:09.840
of the competition.

29:09.920 --> 29:11.920
Let's welcome the award presenter,

29:12.000 --> 29:13.920
the representative of A Dream of Jianghu,

29:14.000 --> 29:15.200
Mr. Duan Jiaxu,

29:15.280 --> 29:16.320
onto the stage.

29:16.400 --> 29:17.960
Applause, please.

29:30.040 --> 29:32.200
Hello, everyone. I am Duan Jiaxu.

29:32.280 --> 29:34.480
It's my great honor to represent

29:34.560 --> 29:36.440
the production team of A Dream of Jianghu

29:36.520 --> 29:38.240
and present awards to everyone today.

29:38.320 --> 29:39.640
You're so handsome!

29:40.120 --> 29:42.080
Man, the new game is so much fun!

29:42.160 --> 29:43.680
Boss, are you still single?

30:04.400 --> 30:05.400
Sorry, everyone.

30:05.920 --> 30:07.840
My girlfriend is taking a photo of me.

30:08.440 --> 30:10.120
She has a clearer view now.

30:13.600 --> 30:14.880
He's so sweet!

30:14.960 --> 30:16.080
Goodness!

30:18.080 --> 30:19.160
Let's get back to business.

30:19.240 --> 30:21.760
I will be presenting

30:21.840 --> 30:23.720
the last award of this competition.

30:24.280 --> 30:26.680
The Character Image Design Award.

30:26.760 --> 30:28.480
Please take a look at the screen.

30:28.560 --> 30:31.240
THE FIFTH DESIGN COMPETITION
OF YIHE UNIVERSITY

30:31.320 --> 30:32.240
So cute.

30:32.320 --> 30:33.560
"MY SECRET" BY SANG ZHI

30:38.760 --> 30:40.080
Then let's keep at it

30:40.160 --> 30:41.480
and work hard together.

30:42.280 --> 30:44.040
I will find my dream.

30:45.080 --> 30:47.240
You will also realize your dream soon.

30:48.880 --> 30:50.280
I hope

30:50.360 --> 30:52.640
that all unhappy things
can stay away from you.

30:52.720 --> 30:55.240
I hope that someone can accompany you.

30:55.800 --> 30:57.560
I hope that someone is me.

30:57.640 --> 30:59.320
It's very creative.

30:59.400 --> 31:00.680
It's so good.

31:01.960 --> 31:05.120
Now our dreams

31:05.200 --> 31:06.760
have come true.

31:24.200 --> 31:25.680
Now,

31:25.760 --> 31:27.760
let's invite this award-winning student,

31:28.320 --> 31:30.360
Sang Zhi, to come to the stage
to accept the award.

31:32.760 --> 31:34.080
Great job, Sang Zhi!

31:34.160 --> 31:35.480
Awesome!

31:39.840 --> 31:40.800
Great!

32:01.480 --> 32:02.520
Congratulations.

32:06.320 --> 32:07.480
Thank you.

32:07.560 --> 32:08.400
Next up,

32:08.480 --> 32:10.040
let's invite the winners

32:10.120 --> 32:11.880
and the dean of Yihe University

32:11.960 --> 32:12.920
onto the stage

32:13.000 --> 32:14.240
to take a group photo

32:14.320 --> 32:15.720
with Mr. Duan Jiaxu.

32:15.800 --> 32:16.640
Please come up.

32:22.120 --> 32:23.200
Hello. Thank you.

32:27.360 --> 32:28.400
Everyone on stage,

32:28.480 --> 32:30.240
please face the camera in the center.

32:30.320 --> 32:31.680
Get ready for a big group photo.

32:31.760 --> 32:32.720
Get ready.

32:33.480 --> 32:35.440
Three, two,

32:35.520 --> 32:36.520
one.

32:36.600 --> 32:38.680
AWARD CERTIFICATE

32:55.000 --> 32:59.200
TWO YEARS LATER

33:00.960 --> 33:04.360
- Happy graduation!
- Happy graduation!

33:04.440 --> 33:06.240
- Happy graduation!
- Happy graduation!

33:07.480 --> 33:09.160
- Graduation dance!
- Okay!

33:09.240 --> 33:10.640
- I'll help you take pictures.
- Okay!

33:51.320 --> 33:52.680
- Who?
- Come at me!

33:55.440 --> 33:56.320
Over there.

33:57.120 --> 33:58.200
Let's take photos of them.

34:32.960 --> 34:34.520
Four years went by so fast.

34:35.360 --> 34:36.199
We've graduated.

34:36.280 --> 34:37.360
Stop right there.

34:38.120 --> 34:39.639
I don't want to cry today.

34:39.719 --> 34:40.960
Don't tell me what to do.

34:41.719 --> 34:43.280
Normally, I would argue with you.

34:43.960 --> 34:45.560
But today,

34:46.280 --> 34:47.679
we'll go our separate ways soon.

34:47.760 --> 34:48.600
I'll shut up.

34:49.480 --> 34:51.400
What am I going to do

34:51.480 --> 34:52.639
without you bickering with me?

34:52.719 --> 34:54.679
Isn't Chen Qiang also good
at talking back?

34:55.239 --> 34:56.320
Would he dare?

34:57.720 --> 34:59.200
I might not get used to it either.

35:00.760 --> 35:02.800
I want to cry even more now!

35:02.880 --> 35:03.960
Don't cry!

35:04.040 --> 35:05.080
I can't take it!

35:05.160 --> 35:06.560
All right, it's fine.

35:07.040 --> 35:08.440
Although we have graduated,

35:09.400 --> 35:11.520
we were only together for four years,

35:12.480 --> 35:13.360
and

35:14.840 --> 35:16.000
it was fleeting,

35:17.080 --> 35:19.880
our friendship won't disappear.

35:22.680 --> 35:24.160
Always together.

35:36.200 --> 35:37.080
Weiwei.

35:38.600 --> 35:40.560
Your makeup is really messed up.

35:40.640 --> 35:42.400
If you want to take pictures later,

35:42.480 --> 35:43.360
you should…

35:43.440 --> 35:44.640
- Where?
- She's right.

35:44.720 --> 35:46.000
Go and fix it.

35:46.080 --> 35:47.680
- I'm going!
- We'll take more photos later.

35:47.760 --> 35:48.960
- Go with her.
- Find a bathroom.

35:49.040 --> 35:49.920
I'll go with you.

35:50.000 --> 35:51.880
- Okay, let's go.
- Did you bring your makeup bag?

35:51.960 --> 35:53.160
- I did.
- Hurry up.

35:53.240 --> 35:55.000
- Fill in your brows now.
- Okay.

35:55.080 --> 35:56.400
- Do you want water?
- Yes, later.

35:56.480 --> 35:57.360
- Later.
- Thank you.

35:57.440 --> 35:58.760
- I'm going to fix my makeup.
- Okay.

35:58.840 --> 36:00.000
Help yourself to water.

36:00.080 --> 36:01.040
- Okay.
- I have it here.

36:01.120 --> 36:01.960
- This way.
- Come on.

36:02.040 --> 36:03.080
- Hurry up.
- Okay.

36:06.760 --> 36:07.840
Let's do it right here.

36:08.440 --> 36:09.320
- Chen Qiang.
- Here.

36:09.400 --> 36:11.800
Do you remember what you're going to say?

36:11.880 --> 36:13.200
- Right.
- Roses!

36:13.280 --> 36:14.800
- Yes, go and get them.
- Go get them.

36:14.880 --> 36:17.240
- Let's make a heart here.
- Give it to me.

36:17.320 --> 36:18.560
Then pile it up.

36:18.640 --> 36:19.880
After it's piled up,

36:19.960 --> 36:21.560
we'll scatter a ring of roses around it.

36:21.640 --> 36:22.960
- Where do we start?
- From here.

36:24.880 --> 36:25.960
Pile it up, right?

36:27.160 --> 36:28.000
Come on.

36:28.840 --> 36:30.000
- I'll help you.
- Okay.

36:30.080 --> 36:31.000
There's too much here.

36:31.080 --> 36:32.920
- Change it.
- It's okay.

36:33.000 --> 36:34.040
This is okay.

36:34.120 --> 36:35.200
We can pile it up now.

36:35.280 --> 36:36.280
Hurry up.

36:36.360 --> 36:37.680
- How should we pile it?
- Like this.

36:37.760 --> 36:39.040
Take it all like this.

36:39.120 --> 36:40.520
- Pile it up, right?
- Yes.

36:40.600 --> 36:41.520
Make a heart

36:41.600 --> 36:42.640
and roses.

36:43.280 --> 36:45.280
So? What do you think?

36:45.360 --> 36:47.040
- It works.
- She will like it.

36:50.240 --> 36:52.160
I hope it works out.

36:54.200 --> 36:55.600
Don't open your eyes.

36:55.680 --> 36:57.040
- What?
- Don't open your eyes.

36:57.120 --> 36:59.280
I just fixed my makeup. Don't mess it up.

36:59.360 --> 37:01.400
That won't happen. I won't touch it.

37:01.480 --> 37:03.200
- Be careful.
- Be careful.

37:03.280 --> 37:05.240
Follow our steps.

37:05.320 --> 37:06.800
Be careful.

37:06.880 --> 37:07.880
Are we there yet?

37:07.960 --> 37:09.240
- We're almost there. Come.
- Come.

37:09.320 --> 37:10.280
- Get ready.
- Take a step.

37:10.360 --> 37:11.520
- Your right foot.
- Take a step.

37:11.600 --> 37:12.640
Which foot?

37:12.720 --> 37:14.080
- This is confusing!
- Be careful.

37:14.880 --> 37:16.000
Okay.

37:16.080 --> 37:17.000
Stand up.

37:17.080 --> 37:18.000
Come here.

37:18.800 --> 37:19.640
Are you ready?

37:19.720 --> 37:20.880
- Ready.
- Ready.

37:20.960 --> 37:21.800
- Okay.
- Three.

37:21.880 --> 37:22.760
Two!

37:22.840 --> 37:23.960
- One!
- One!

37:55.480 --> 37:57.520
Sorry, this is a bit abrupt.

37:58.760 --> 38:01.360
I thought of many different ways.

38:07.280 --> 38:08.160
Sang Zhi.

38:09.960 --> 38:11.440
In the past, I always felt

38:11.520 --> 38:13.160
that being alone forever

38:13.640 --> 38:14.840
wouldn't matter much to me.

38:16.160 --> 38:17.400
That was until I met you.

38:18.600 --> 38:20.040
You made me realize

38:20.600 --> 38:23.240
that loving someone and being loved

38:23.960 --> 38:25.760
is such a happy thing.

38:33.600 --> 38:35.400
Thank you for giving me so much love.

38:36.880 --> 38:37.960
Because of you,

38:38.600 --> 38:39.960
I found out

38:41.000 --> 38:42.720
that I'm such a great person too.

38:44.320 --> 38:45.560
It turns out

38:46.600 --> 38:48.320
that I deserve to be loved too.

39:01.040 --> 39:03.080
You made me suddenly want to try.

39:04.680 --> 39:06.320
To love someone no matter what.

39:28.040 --> 39:29.960
I don't have anything else I can give you.

39:31.200 --> 39:32.240
Only six words.

39:33.800 --> 39:35.800
Only one person for a lifetime.

39:37.840 --> 39:40.440
I hope you can be a witness
to these six words.

39:41.320 --> 39:43.800
But it will take
a little longer to witness.

39:44.600 --> 39:45.960
I want to use a lifetime

39:46.840 --> 39:48.240
to live up to this promise.

39:56.600 --> 39:57.880
Will you marry me?

40:01.720 --> 40:03.440
- Say yes!
- Say yes!

40:03.520 --> 40:05.520
- Say yes!
- Marry him!

40:11.440 --> 40:12.320
Sangsang!

40:19.560 --> 40:20.480
Sangsang!

40:40.360 --> 40:41.360
Kiss!

40:41.440 --> 40:44.320
- Kiss!
- Kiss!

41:21.000 --> 41:22.440
I am quite envious of you.

41:24.720 --> 41:26.680
You secretly liked me for so long.

41:28.720 --> 41:31.200
The feeling of having a person in my heart

41:31.280 --> 41:32.160
is quite nice.

41:36.320 --> 41:37.640
I'll tell you a secret.

41:40.200 --> 41:42.520
Before I told you that I liked you,

41:43.920 --> 41:45.400
I already secretly liked you.

41:48.040 --> 41:48.920
Really?

41:56.040 --> 41:57.440
Do you still remember

41:57.520 --> 41:59.160
the first snowfall in your freshman year?

42:00.000 --> 42:01.320
That was when it started.

42:10.600 --> 42:11.880
Our story started

42:12.880 --> 42:14.600
when he was 22 years old.

42:18.680 --> 42:21.680
I used to secretly hide
my feelings for him.

42:23.040 --> 42:24.840
I didn't dare to let anyone find out.

42:30.720 --> 42:32.480
I strived to become a better person

42:33.160 --> 42:34.560
and catch up to him.

42:41.480 --> 42:43.280
When I made it to his side,

42:44.040 --> 42:45.120
I found out

42:47.600 --> 42:49.560
that I was never running alone.

42:51.680 --> 42:53.440
He was also running towards me.

42:57.520 --> 42:59.440
It was five full years.

43:03.160 --> 43:05.520
I healed the wounds of his youth.

43:07.120 --> 43:10.640
He fulfilled my young first love.

43:32.320 --> 43:33.600
Our story started

43:34.840 --> 43:36.720
